== 0.0.3 - 21-Aug-2009
* Changed the license to Artistic 2.0.
* Removed C related code from the Rakefile. Also, the original C code has been
  sent to its own branch in the repository.
* Updates to the gemspec, including the license and description.
* Renamed the test and example files.

== 0.0.2 - 18-May-2008
* This library is now pure Ruby, using the windows-pr library.
* Added a Rakefile with tasks for installation and testing.
* Added a gemspec and a gem file.
* Moved the C source files. These are in the SCM repository, but are not
  included as part of the release.
* Merged the doc files into the README. The API documentation is now inlined,
  so it can be generated automatically.

== 0.0.1 - 13-Dec-2004
* Initial release
